    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action or state of achieving a state of greater knowledge, understanding, or insight. For example, in Buddhism, it is the state of spiritual insight or awareness which frees a person from the cycle of suffering and rebirth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
